    <!--
    Adding a string to the resource file:
    When you add a string to this file, add a comment to the side saying this:
    <!- TRANSLATE: [list of languages to translate this string into] ->
    Then, message those who are doing translations for the languages the string needs 
    to be translated into.
    This is to make sure we do not miss any strings that need to be translated.
