                                            etc. it can only edit plain text documents (.txt)</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ap_desc_web_browser">For viewing web pages. You can bookmark pages for easy access later.
                                               There are two versions of the web browser, one which uses a button 
                                               grid for interaction and one which depends on using the Windows Eye 
                                               Control bar. You can switch between these two from Display Settings.</system:String>
